Class SimpleCaseResult

  • java.lang.Object

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    hudson.model.ModelObject, hudson.search.SearchableModelObject, hudson.search.SearchItem, java.io.Serializable
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    TrivialTestResult

    public class SimpleCaseResult
extends TestResult
    The simplest possible case result, with no language ties. Acts as if it passed, has no children, and has no failed or skipped tests.
    See Also:
